If you have a secret insider trading code for your text messages, don=E2=80=
=99t=C2=A0explain the code in the text messages, come on.
Anyway though the FBI eventually did come calling. Viggiano was not worried=
:
On or around June 27, 2023=E2=80=94after the trading by Salamone based on m=
aterial=C2=A0nonpublic information from Viggiano, alleged below=E2=80=94Vig=
giano told Salamone that he had been approached by law enforcement. Viggian=
